---
// src/components/AboutSection.astro
---
<div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        
        <div class="relative group">
            <div
                class="absolute -inset-4 rounded-3xl opacity-20 blur-xl transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover:opacity-30"
                style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7dd3fc 0%, #38bdf8 50%, #0ea5e9 100%);"
            >
            </div>
            <img
                src="/src/assets/img/NosotrosImagen.jpg" 
                alt="Equipo DIVCAL"
                class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            />
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
                <div class="mb-8 md:mb-12">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="w-16 md:w-24 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></div>

                        <span class="font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-sky-600" style="letter-spacing: 0.2em;">
                            Quiénes Somos
                        </span>

                        <div class="w-16 md:w-24 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">
                    Conoce <span class="text-sky-500">DIVCAL</span>
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
                    En <span class="font-semibold text-sky-600">DIVCAL PE</span> nos especializamos en soluciones 
                    <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">BPO de Contact Center Omnicanal</span>...
                </p>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
                    Trabajamos mano a mano con empresas de diversos sectores...
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="relative mt-10">
                <div class="absolute -top-5 left-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-sky-500">
                    <svg class="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                        <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>

                <blockquote class="pl-12 pt-2 text-xl font-medium italic text-sky-700">
                    "Transformamos desafíos operativos en ventajas competitivas sostenibles"
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    @keyframes float {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
    }
    .group:hover .absolute.-inset-4 {
        animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
</style>